title: Mominoki House Food Concept Shop
typeOfFood: Vegan-friendly, International, Japanese, Macrobiotic, Organic, Beer/Wine, Fusion, Non-veg
description: Serves meat, veg options available. Reported in 2013 after brief closure. Offers an array of choices from extravagant hemp tofu to a simple bowl of brown rice, electron-charged soy ice cream "tofu blamagae," black sesame tofu-ice with sweet beans, and tofu for dessert. Address in Japanese: 東京都渋谷区神宮前2-18-5. Directions: Harajuku Station, Meiji Street by Jingumae ichomae junction, turn right.
